727385f-a.title: Queens: Metropolitan Ave - at intersection of Cooper Ave
727385f-a.text:
Metropolitan Ave., south side, at its intersection with Cooper Ave.
showing the Saflian Jaeger farmhouse and outbuildings. Some of the owners
were:Jaflian Jaeger 1873, G. Yeager 1891, L. Whitemeyer 1896, and one
Berkaeyer in 1909. A gas station occupied its site in 1929. This is a
set of two views.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)  Another and more distant view of the house, seen from
Woodhaven Bodlevard.
Eugene L. Armbruster Cotiection
MAY BE REPRODUCED
April, 1923
